import React, { useState, useEffect, } from 'react'; import './BusinessSearch.css'; const BusinessSearchPage = () => { const [searchParams, setSearchParams] = useState({ city: '', state_abreviation: '', name: '', postal_code: '', stars: '', review_count: '', is_open: false, accepts_insurance: false, by_appointment_only: false, accept_creditcard: false, garage_parking: false, lot_parking: false, street_parking: false, valet_parking: false, bYOB: false, open_24_hours: false, accepts_bitcoin: false, dogs_allowed: false, drive_thru: false, delivery: false, outdoor_seating: false, good_for_dancing: false, happy_hour: false, take_out: false, reservations: false, wifi: false, good_for_groups: false, casual: false, upscale: false, trendy: false, touristy: false, divey: false, hipster: false, classy: false, intimate: false, romantic: false, alcohol: false, }); const config = require('../config.json') const [searchResults, setSearchResults] = useState([]); const handleChange = (e) => { const { name, value, type, checked } = e.target; setSearchParams((prevParams) => ({ ...prevParams, [name]: type === 'checkbox' ? checked : value, })); }; useEffect(() => { handleSubmit(); }, []); const handleSubmit = () => { // Make API request here console.log("Client-side: Fetching data with search parameters:", searchParams); console.log("Client-side: The URL:", new URLSearchParams(searchParams).toString()); fetch (`http://${config.server_host}:${config.server_port}/search/businesses?${new URLSearchParams(searchParams).toString()}`) .then((res) => res.json()) .then((resJson) => setSearchResults(resJson)) .catch((error) => console.log("Error fetching data:", error)) // const response = await fetch(`/search/businesses?${new URLSearchParams(searchParams).toString()}`); // console.log("Waiting for data from server:", response); // const data = await response.json(); // console.log("Received data from server:", data); // setSearchResults(data); }; return (

Business Search

Search Results

    {searchResults.map((business) => (
  • {business.name} - {business.stars} stars
    • ))}
); }; export default BusinessSearchPage;
